{
  "texts": [
    "The LSTM model's performance shows a stark contrast between the datasets for Malaysia and the UAE.",
    "For Malaysia, the model exhibited a robust R2 score of 0.8985, which was significantly higher than the mean 0.004 score for the UAE.",
    "It seems to be far more accurate in capturing the underlying patterns in the Malaysian dataset, as indicated by the substantially lower MAE of 0.0064 compared to 0.046 for the UAE.",
    "Therefore, in terms of the overall performance, the LSTM model showed a clear propensity for stronger predictive accuracy with the Malaysian dataset.",
    "Bi-LSTM also demonstrates better efficacy for the Malaysian dataset."
  ]
}